  "culturalTip": "You will see a multitude of cosmetic stores while walking down the street in Korea. Most stores have good quality and affordable products. In addition to cosmetic stores, there are also drugstores. Drugstores carry affordable cosmetics and skincare products from Korea as well as other countries, such as Japan, France, or Germany. If you are looking to purchase more luxury or high-end brands of cosmetics or skincare products, visit a department store.",
